Class ChangeMenuPreparePluginController

java.lang.Object
edu.jiangxin.apktoolbox.swing.extend.plugin.ChangeMenuPreparePluginController
All Implemented Interfaces:
IPreparePluginCallback
public class ChangeMenuPreparePluginController extends Object implements IPreparePluginCallback
This class is used to prepare plugin for change menu.

All operations in this class will be executed in main thread.
